    "body": "My personal preference would be to have it go off a _bit_ sooner, i.e. Mar 2022. There may be a world where everything goes right and we are ready to do the merge in Q4 2021 / Q1 2022. If we are not ready then, we can also push the bomb back again by a short amount. In other words, I'd rather have it go off sooner, and be pushed out once more after this, than have it scheduled too late and we're waiting for it for the merge. ",
